n be exploited to produce\nhighly-sensitive responses, making such systems good candidates for sensor\napplications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 17:18:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Jun 2018 09:16:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-28"}
