bility, we constrain\nthe magnetic field of the emission region to be a few gauss; whereas in\nflat-spectrum radio quasars, using external Compton models, we estimate the\nenergy of the lower end of the injected electrons to be a few Lorentz factors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 21:12:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Aug 2018 07:56:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
