ssfully employed to analyze\necological as well as economic systems, thus representing an ideal,\ninterdisciplinary tool to approach the study of bipartite complex systems.\n[...]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Oct 2017 14:12:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-20"}
